<i>noun</i>: 통사정 [통사정] <i>verb</i>: 호소하다 [호소하다], 통사정하다 [통사정하다], 애원하다 [애원하다], 소청하다 [소청하다], 사정하다 [사ː정하다], 사정사정하다 [사ː정사정하다], 간청하다 [간ː청하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>통사정 [통사정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. plead; beg; appeal</dd><br>
<dd>딱하고 어려운 형편을 털어놓으면서 사정함.</dd><br>
<dd>To explain one's pitiful and difficult situation to someone and ask for help or a favor.</dd><br>
<dd>2. have a frank talk</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 자신의 생각을 표현함.</dd><br>
<dd>To express one's thoughts to someone.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호소하다 [호소하다]</dt><br>
<dd>appeal; plead</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 어렵거나 억울한 사정을 다른 사람에게 알려 도움을 청하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To ask another for help by describing one's situation to someone such as unfair treatment, difficulties, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>통사정하다 [통사정하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. plead; beg; appeal</dd><br>
<dd>딱하고 어려운 형편을 털어놓으면서 사정하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To explain one's pitiful and difficult situation to someone and ask for help or a favor.</dd><br>
<dd>2. have a frank talk</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 자신의 생각을 표현하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To express one's thoughts to someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>애원하다 [애원하다]</dt><br>
<dd>plead; implore</dd><br>
<dd>요청이나 소원을 들어 달라고 애처롭게 사정하여 간절히 부탁하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To beg someone earnestly and pathetically to meet a person's demands or do something that he/she wishes for.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소청하다 [소청하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. request; plead</dd><br>
<dd>사정을 말하며 부탁하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a request to someone while explaining one's own situation.</dd><br>
<dd>2. petition</dd><br>
<dd>징계 처분을 받은 공무원이 그 처분에 따르지 않고 취소나 변경 등을 청구하다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a government officer, who is the subject of a disciplinary action, to ask for its cancellation or change, not obeying the action.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사정하다 [사ː정하다]</dt><br>
<dd>beg; plead</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람에게 일의 형편을 말하고 도와줄 것을 부탁하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To explain the situation of something to someone and ask for his/her help.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사정사정하다 [사ː정사정하다]</dt><br>
<dd>plead; implore; solicit</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람에게 일의 형편을 말하고 도와줄 것을 간절하게 부탁하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To explain one's situation to another person and earnestly ask for his/her help.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>간청하다 [간ː청하다]</dt><br>
<dd>plead; request earnestly; beg</dd><br>
<dd>간절히 부탁하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To plead with someone heartily.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>